<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Update a log shipping token</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"put"} path={"/v1/log-shipping/tokens/{id}"}></MethodEndpoint>



Enables/disables a log shipping token and/or renames it. 
Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.
